Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: My Home
Description: I spent a decade of my life here, from 2007-2017. Now it's my home again, thanks to COVID-19. It's comfortable and safe.

Name: Huntington Beach Pier
Description: Many a weekend was spent here or at nearby Pacific City, falling in love with the ocean and a special person. The city of Huntington Beach has been fighting Santa Cruz for years over the legal rights to the title of "Surf City USA".

Name: Fountain Valley
Description: This is where I had my first kiss, around midnight on a rainy night in the middle of the worst storm in California in years.

Name: Signal Hill
Description: A beautiful place to take in the sights of LA, especially at night.

Name: Oakwood Mountain View
Description: The apartment I stayed in last summer, thanks to my internship. It was a modern 1 bedroom apartment In an incredibly expensive city; I still can't quite believe I Lived here.
